<item chapterid="607406" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1944" articlename="贴身男秘" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521809533" lastupdate="1521809533" chaptername="第327回老爹动情了？" chapterorder="328" size="6177" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    郑焰红有点傻眼了，她愣愣的问道：“爹，人家咋闯祸了？”

